2. Brief Description

This project demonstrates various multithreading concepts in Java, including:
- Thread pool management with ExecutorService.
- Concurrent execution of multiple threads (Table printing).
- Random character generation with fluctuating sleep times.
- Synchronization mechanisms for shared resources (Joint Bank Account).
- Inter-thread communication using wait() and notify() (Printer Job).
- Deadlock detection and resolution using consistent lock ordering.

